:- encoding(utf8).
% Lore local da geracao 1
% Formato: pokemon_lore(ID, Texto).
:- multifile pokemon_lore/2.
pokemon_lore(1, 'It can go for days without eating a single morsel. In the bulb on its back, it stores energy.').
pokemon_lore(2, 'The bulb on its back grows by drawing energy. It gives off an aroma when it is ready to bloom.').
pokemon_lore(3, 'The flower on its back catches the sun''s rays. The sunlight is then absorbed and used for energy.').
pokemon_lore(4, 'The flame at the tip of its tail makes a sound as it burns. You can only hear it in quiet places.').
pokemon_lore(5, 'Tough fights could excite this POKéMON. When excited, it may blow out bluish- white flames.').
pokemon_lore(6, 'When expelling a blast of super hot fire, the red flame at the tip of its tail burns more intensely.').
pokemon_lore(7, 'Shoots water at prey while in the water. Withdraws into its shell when in danger.').
pokemon_lore(8, 'When tapped, this POKéMON will pull in its head, but its tail will still stick out a little bit.').
pokemon_lore(9, 'Once it takes aim at its enemy, it blasts out water with even more force than a fire hose.').
pokemon_lore(10, 'If you touch the feeler on top of its head, it will release a horrible stink to protect itself.').
pokemon_lore(11, 'Hardens its shell to protect itself. However, a large impact may cause it to pop out of its shell.').
pokemon_lore(12, 'Its wings, covered with poisonous powders, repel water. This allows it to fly in the rain.').
pokemon_lore(13, 'Beware of the sharp stinger on its head. It hides in grass and bushes where it eats leaves.').
pokemon_lore(14, 'Able to move only slightly. When endangered, it may stick out its stinger and poison its enemy.').
pokemon_lore(15, 'It has 3 poisonous stingers on its forelegs and its tail. They are used to jab its enemy repeatedly.').
pokemon_lore(16, 'Very docile. If attacked, it will often kick up sand to protect itself rather than fight back.').
pokemon_lore(17, 'This POKéMON is full of vitality. It constantly flies around its large territory in search of prey.').
pokemon_lore(18, 'This POKéMON flies at Mach 2 speed, seeking prey. Its large talons are feared as wicked weapons.').
pokemon_lore(19, 'Will chew on any­ thing with its fangs. If you see one, it is certain that 40 more live in the area.').
pokemon_lore(20, 'Its hind feet are webbed. They act as flippers, so it can swim in rivers and hunt for prey.').
pokemon_lore(21, 'Inept at flying high. However, it can fly around very fast to protect its ter­ ritory.').
pokemon_lore(22, 'A POKéMON that dates back many years. If it senses danger, it flies high and away, instantly.').
pokemon_lore(23, 'The older it gets, the longer it grows. At night, it wraps its long body around tree branches to rest.').
pokemon_lore(24, 'The frightening patterns on its belly have been studied. Six variations have been confirmed.').
pokemon_lore(25, 'It keeps its tail raised to monitor its surroundings. If you yank its tail, it will try to bite you.').
pokemon_lore(26, 'When electricity builds up inside its body, it becomes feisty. It also glows in the dark.').
pokemon_lore(27, 'Its body is dry. When it gets cold at night, its hide is said to become coated with a fine dew.').
pokemon_lore(28, 'It is skilled at slashing enemies with its claws. If broken, they start to grow back in a day.').
pokemon_lore(29, 'A mild-mannered POKéMON that does not like to fight. Beware, its small horns secrete venom.').
pokemon_lore(30, 'When resting deep in its burrow, its thorns always retract. This is proof that it is relaxed.').
pokemon_lore(31, 'Tough scales cover the sturdy body of this POKéMON. It appears that the scales grow in cycles.').
pokemon_lore(32, 'Its large ears are always kept upright. If it senses danger, it will attack with a poisonous sting.').
pokemon_lore(33, 'Its horns contain venom. If they are stabbed into an enemy, the impact makes the poison leak out.').
pokemon_lore(34, 'Its steel-like hide adds to its powerful tackle. Its horns are so hard, they can pierce a diamond.').
pokemon_lore(35, 'Adored for their cute looks and playfulness. They are thought to be rare, as they do not appear often.').
pokemon_lore(36, 'They appear to be very protective of their own world. It is a kind of fairy, rarely seen by people.').
pokemon_lore(37, 'Both its fur and its tails are beautiful. As it grows, the tails split and form more tails.').
pokemon_lore(38, 'According to an enduring legend, 9 noble saints were united and reincarnated as this POKéMON.').
pokemon_lore(39, 'Uses its alluring eyes to enrapture its foe. It then sings a pleasing melody that lulls the foe to sleep.').
pokemon_lore(40, 'Its body is full of elasticity. By inhaling deeply, it can continue to inflate itself without limit.').
pokemon_lore(41, 'Emits ultrasonic cries while it flies. They act as a sonar used to check for ob­ jects in its way.').
pokemon_lore(42, 'It attacks in a stealthy manner, without warning. Its sharp fangs are used to bite and suck blood.').
pokemon_lore(43, 'It may be mistaken for a clump of weeds. If you try to yank it out of the ground, it shrieks horribly.').
pokemon_lore(44, 'Smells incredibly foul! However, around 1 out of 1,000 people enjoy sniffing its nose- bending stink.').
pokemon_lore(45, 'Flaps its broad flower petals to scatter its poisonous pollen. The flapping sound is very loud.').
pokemon_lore(46, 'Burrows under the ground to gnaw on tree roots. The mushrooms on its back absorb most of the nutrition.').
pokemon_lore(47, 'The bug host is drained of energy by the mushrooms on its back. They appear to do all the thinking.').
pokemon_lore(48, 'Its large eyes act as radars. In a bright place, you can see that they are clusters of many tiny eyes.').
pokemon_lore(49, 'The powdery scales on its wings are hard to remove. They also contain poison that leaks out on contact.').
pokemon_lore(50, 'It prefers dark places. It spends most of its time underground, though it may pop up in caves.').
pokemon_lore(51, 'A team of triplets that can burrow over 60 MPH. Due to this, some people think it''s an earthquake.').
pokemon_lore(52, 'Appears to be more active at night. It loves round and shiny things. It can''t stop from picking them up.').
pokemon_lore(53, 'The gem in its forehead glows on its own! It walks with all the grace and elegance of a proud queen.').
pokemon_lore(54, 'Always tormented by headaches. It uses psychic powers, but it is not known if it intends to do so.').
pokemon_lore(55, 'Its slim and long limbs end in broad flippers. They are used for swim­ ming gracefully in lakes.').
pokemon_lore(56, 'An agile POKéMON that lives in trees. It angers easily and will not hesitate to attack anything.').
pokemon_lore(57, 'It stops being angry only when nobody else is around. To view this moment is very difficult.').
pokemon_lore(58, 'A POKéMON with a friendly nature. However, it will bark fiercely at anything invading its territory.').
pokemon_lore(59, 'A legendary POKé­ MON in China. Many people are charmed by its grace and beauty while running.').
pokemon_lore(60, 'The direction of the spiral on the belly differs by area. It is more adept at swimming than walking.').
pokemon_lore(61, 'Under attack, it uses its belly spiral to put the foe to sleep. It then makes its escape.').
pokemon_lore(62, 'Swims powerfully using all the muscles in its body. It can even overtake champion swimmers.').
pokemon_lore(63, 'Sleeps 18 hours a day. If it senses danger, it will teleport itself to safety even as it sleeps.').
pokemon_lore(64, 'Many odd things happen if this POKéMON is close by. For example, it makes clocks run backwards.').
pokemon_lore(65, 'A POKéMON that can memorize anything. It never forgets what it learns-- that''s why this POKéMON is smart.').
pokemon_lore(66, 'Very powerful in spite of its small size. Its mastery of many types of martial arts makes it very tough.').
pokemon_lore(67, 'The belt around its waist holds back its energy. Without it, this POKéMON would be unstoppable.').
pokemon_lore(68, 'One arm alone can move mountains. Using all four arms, this POKéMON fires off awesome punches.').
pokemon_lore(69, 'Prefers hot and humid places. It ensnares tiny insects with its vines and devours them.').
pokemon_lore(70, 'When hungry, it swallows anything that moves. Its hapless prey is melted inside by strong acids.').
pokemon_lore(71, 'Lures prey with the sweet aroma of honey. Swallowed whole, the prey is melted in a day, bones and all.').
pokemon_lore(72, 'It can sometimes be found all dry and shriveled up on a beach. Toss it back into the sea to revive it.').
pokemon_lore(73, 'Its 80 tentacles can stretch and contract freely. They wrap around prey and weaken it with poison.').
pokemon_lore(74, 'Commonly found near mountain trails, etc. If you step on one by accident, it gets angry.').
pokemon_lore(75, 'Often seen rolling down mountain trails. Obstacles are just things to roll straight over, not avoid.').
pokemon_lore(76, 'Once it sheds its skin, its body turns tender and whitish. Its hide hardens when it''s exposed to air.').
pokemon_lore(77, 'Capable of jumping incredibly high. Its hooves and sturdy legs absorb the impact of a hard landing.').
pokemon_lore(78, 'Just loves to run. If it sees some­ thing faster than itself, it will give chase at top speed.').
pokemon_lore(79, 'Incredibly slow and sluggish. It is quite content to loll about without worrying about the time.').
pokemon_lore(80, 'Lives lazily by the sea. If the SHELLDER on its tail comes off, it becomes a SLOWPOKE again.').
pokemon_lore(81, 'It is born with the ability to defy gravity. It floats in air on powerful electro­ magnetic waves.').
pokemon_lore(82, 'Generates strange radio signals. It raises the tem­ perature by 3.6F degrees within 3,300 feet.').
pokemon_lore(83, 'Lives where reedy plants grow. They are rarely seen, so it''s thought their numbers are decreasing.').
pokemon_lore(84, 'Its short wings make flying dif­ ficult. Instead, this POKéMON runs at high speed on developed legs.').
pokemon_lore(85, 'One of DODUO''s 2 heads splits to form a unique species. It runs close to 40 MPH in prairies.').
pokemon_lore(86, 'Loves freezing cold conditions. Relishes swimming in a frigid cli­ mate of around 14F degrees.').
pokemon_lore(87, 'Its entire body is a snowy-white. Unharmed by even intense cold, it swims powerfully in icy waters.').
pokemon_lore(88, 'Made of hardened sludge. It smells too putrid to touch. Even weeds won''t grow in its path.').
pokemon_lore(89, 'Smells so awful, it can cause fainting. Through degeneration, it lost its sense of smell.').
pokemon_lore(90, 'The shell can withstand any attack. However, when it is open, the tender body is exposed.').
pokemon_lore(91, 'For protection, it uses its harder- than-diamonds shell. It also shoots spikes from the shell.').
pokemon_lore(92, 'Said to appear in decrepit, deserted buildings. It has no real shape as it appears to be made of a gas.').
pokemon_lore(93, 'By licking, it saps the victim''s life. It causes shaking that won''t stop until the victim''s demise.').
pokemon_lore(94, 'A GENGAR is close by if you feel a sudden chill. It may be trying to lay a curse on you.').
pokemon_lore(95, 'Burrows at high speed in search of food. The tunnels it leaves are used as homes by DIGLETTs.').
pokemon_lore(96, 'If you sleep by it all the time, it will sometimes show you dreams it has eaten in the past.').
pokemon_lore(97, 'Avoid eye contact if you come across one. It will try to put you to sleep by using its pendulum.').
pokemon_lore(98, 'Its pincers are superb weapons. They sometimes break off during battle, but they grow back fast.').
pokemon_lore(99, 'One claw grew massively and as hard as steel. It has 10,000-HP strength. However, it is too heavy.').
pokemon_lore(100, 'It is said to camouflage itself as a POKé BALL. It will self-destruct with very little stimulus.').
pokemon_lore(101, 'Stores electrical energy inside its body. Even the slightest shock could trigger a huge explosion.').
pokemon_lore(102, 'The heads attract each other and spin around. There must be 6 heads for it to maintain balance.').
pokemon_lore(103, 'Its cries are very noisy. This is because each of the 3 heads thinks about whatever it likes.').
pokemon_lore(104, 'Wears the skull of its deceased mother. Its cries echo inside the skull and come out as a sad melody.').
pokemon_lore(105, 'Small and weak, this POKéMON is adept with its bone club. It has grown more vicious over the ages.').
pokemon_lore(106, 'When kicking, the sole of its foot turns as hard as a diamond on im­ pact and destroys its enemy.').
pokemon_lore(107, 'Punches in cork­ screw fashion. It can punch its way through a concrete wall in the same way as a drill.').
pokemon_lore(108, 'Its tongue spans almost 7 feet and moves more freely than its forelegs. Its licks can cause paralysis.').
pokemon_lore(109, 'In hot places, its internal gases could expand and explode without any warning. Be very careful!').
pokemon_lore(110, 'It lives and grows by absorbing dust, germs and poison gases that are contained in toxic waste and garbage.').
pokemon_lore(111, 'A POKéMON with a one-track mind. Once it charges, it won''t stop running until it falls asleep.').
pokemon_lore(112, 'Walks on its hind legs. Shows signs of intelligence. Its armor-like hide even repels molten lava.').
pokemon_lore(113, 'A gentle and kind­ hearted POKéMON that shares its nutritious eggs if it sees an injured POKéMON.').
pokemon_lore(114, 'Its identity is obscured by masses of thick, blue vines. The vines are said to never stop growing.').
pokemon_lore(115, 'Raises its young in its belly pouch. Won''t run from any fight to keep its young protected.').
pokemon_lore(116, 'If it senses any danger, it will vigorously spray water or a special type of ink from its mouth.').
pokemon_lore(117, 'Touching the back fin causes numb­ ness. It hooks its tail to coral to stay in place while sleeping.').
pokemon_lore(118, 'When it is time for them to lay eggs, they can be seen swimming up rivers and falls in large groups.').
pokemon_lore(119, 'It is the male''s job to make a nest by carving out boulders in a stream using the horn on its head.').
pokemon_lore(120, 'As long as the center section is unharmed, it can grow back fully even if it is chopped to bits.').
pokemon_lore(121, 'The center section is named the core. People think it is communicating when it glows in 7 colors.').
pokemon_lore(122, 'Always practices its pantomime act. It makes enemies believe something exists that really doesn''t.').
pokemon_lore(123, 'Leaps out of tall grass and slices prey with its scythes. The move­ ment looks like that of a ninja.').
pokemon_lore(124, 'Appears to move to a rhythm of its own, as if it were dancing. It wiggles its hips as it walks.').
pokemon_lore(125, 'If a major power outage occurs, it is certain that this POKéMON has eaten electricity at a power plant.').
pokemon_lore(126, 'Born in an active volcano. Its body is always cloaked in flames, so it looks like a big ball of fire.').
pokemon_lore(127, 'Grips its prey in its pincers and squeezes hard! It can''t move if it''s cold, so it lives in warm places.').
pokemon_lore(128, 'A rowdy POKéMON with a lot of stamina. Once running, it won''t stop until it hits something.').
pokemon_lore(129, 'Famous for being very unreliable. It can be found swimming in seas, lakes, rivers and shallow puddles.').
pokemon_lore(130, 'Brutally vicious and enormously destructive. Known for totally destroying cities in ancient times.').
pokemon_lore(131, 'A gentle soul that can read the minds of people. It can ferry people across the sea on its back.').
pokemon_lore(132, 'When it spots an enemy, its body transfigures into an almost perfect copy of its oppo­ nent.').
pokemon_lore(133, 'Its genetic code is unstable, so it could evolve in a variety of ways. There are only a few alive.').
pokemon_lore(134, 'Its cell structure is similar to water molecules. It will melt away and become invis­ ible in water.').
pokemon_lore(135, 'A sensitive POKé­ MON that easily becomes sad or angry. Every time its mood changes, it charges power.').
pokemon_lore(136, 'It has a flame chamber inside its body. It inhales, then blows out fire that is over 3,000F degrees.').
pokemon_lore(137, 'The only POKéMON people anticipate can fly into space. None has managed the feat yet, however.').
pokemon_lore(138, 'An ancient POKéMON that was recovered from a fossil. It swims by cleverly twisting its 10 tentacles about.').
pokemon_lore(139, 'Sharp beaks ring its mouth. Its shell was too big for it to move freely, so it became extinct.').
pokemon_lore(140, 'A POKéMON that was recovered from a fossil. It uses the eyes on its back while hiding on the sea floor.').
pokemon_lore(141, 'A slim and fast swimmer. It slices its prey with its sharp sickles and drinks the body fluids.').
pokemon_lore(142, 'A savage POKéMON that died out in ancient times. It was resurrected using DNA taken from amber.').
pokemon_lore(143, 'Will eat anything, even if the food happens to be a little moldy. It never gets an upset stomach.').
pokemon_lore(144, 'A legendary bird POKéMON. It freezes water that is contained in winter air and makes it snow.').
pokemon_lore(145, 'This legendary bird POKéMON is said to appear when the sky turns dark and lightning showers down.').
pokemon_lore(146, 'A legendary bird POKéMON. As it flaps its flaming wings, even the night sky will turn red.').
pokemon_lore(147, 'The existence of this mythical POKéMON was only recently confirmed by a fisherman who caught one.').
pokemon_lore(148, 'According to a witness, its body was surrounded by a strange aura that gave it a mystical look.').
pokemon_lore(149, 'It is said that this POKéMON lives somewhere in the sea and that it flies. However, it is only a rumor.').
pokemon_lore(150, 'Its DNA is almost the same as MEW''s. However, its size and disposition are vastly dif­ ferent.').
pokemon_lore(151, 'When viewed through a micro­ scope, this POKéMON''s short, fine, delicate hair can be seen.').
